de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization

Class Waypoints

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization.Waypoints

  • public class Waypoints
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a Waypoinot object with getters and setters for all the parameters of a DatabaseHelper.waypointsTable Table in Database. Used by WaypointsSync to create a new Waypoint Object to be inserted in to the Database.
    See Also:
    SyncActivity, WaypointsSync, de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization
